about.summary: Automatic error monitoring for django, flask, etc.

name: bugsnag
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "bugsnag" %}
{% set version = "3.6.0" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: "https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz"
  sha256: 67b8c01719e92f193f8424595a94e3a527bc0f9fcb7f2bc47a20af87de81929d

build:
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv"
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3
  run:
    - python >=3
    - six >=1.9,<2
    - webob

test:
  imports:
    - bugsnag

about:
  home: https://bugsnag.com/
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: "Automatic error monitoring for django, flask, etc."
  dev_url: https://github.com/bugsnag/bugsnag-python

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - tschoonj
